content: Hi folks! I'm Nora, @noracodes on twitter and https://nora.codes. I've been doing Rust since, like, 2015, but I've only recently gotten into contributing to the language and open-sourcing a lot of code. I'm excited for the future and I would love to find new places to help out!
Good to see you on Zulip too now!
if you need issues to work on, you can ping me :smile:
